title: Episode 309: 10 On Rotation (Feat. Sean Kingston)
itunes:title: Episode 309: 10 On Rotation (Feat. Sean Kingston)
description:
Singer, Sean Kingston joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his new single "Darkest Times" featuring G Herbo, and things get wild real quick! Sean admits to having 10 girls in rotation, cheating on an ex while she was upstairs in another room, and much more. Sean even stands his ground when the ladies refuse to believe he's never eaten vagina. Enjoy!
